---
title: Smart Chicken and Spinach Coconut Curry with Garlic Bulgur
description: This coconut chicken curry is creamy and spicy, plus you'll love the hints of garlic and ginger! A hearty bed of garlicky bulgur provides a delicious change of pace from the usual rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-de-poulet-a-la-noix-de-coco-dda124de.jpg
